al/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時係現場真係心諗做乜鳩 完全都唔係睇場波<br />\n講埋D野都唔知想點<br />\n<br />\n依家多左隊東方受埋佢地氣 真係好搞笑<br />\n之前大部份都係佢地D自己友 做既野一樣 但照屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前對面隊d球員同球迷d老母都比佢地屌齊曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家真係算好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236db14d370ef5a6fad702c6f7222ae0859835c6","tid":291073,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T16:01:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實永倫個班臭雞唔識波可唔可以收聲<br />\n次次睇現場都聽到佢地勁嘈<br />\n依家連睇直播都聽到佢地把聲<br />\n<br />\n球證已經擺明幫晒永倫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班臭雞當正自己+2gc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上場睇佢地打東方又係咁<br />\n仲要屌兆榮，話佢去東方學壞曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你東方未又係你永倫d舊人組軍<br />\n到阿ga嗰陣又唔敢屌，靜撚曬</blockquote><br />\n有幾個似未食葯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢地根本係睇人唔係睇波<br />\n只要係佢地隊就咩都岩<br />\n唔係佢地隊就咩都屌<br />\n<br />\n依家算好左 早4,5年掉晒野<br />\n唔係話睇波有熱情唔岩 但完全係過晒火<br />\n有年我見羅意庭連入3,4球3分波都被隻臭雞屌<br />\n&quot;屌垃圾 只係識射三分波 返大陸射啦&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當時係現場真係心諗做乜鳩 完全都唔係睇場波<br />\n講埋D野都唔知想點<br />\n<br />\n依家多左隊東方受埋佢地氣 真係好搞笑<br />\n之前大部份都係佢地D自己友 做既野一樣 但照屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前對面隊d球員同球迷d老母都比佢地屌齊曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家真係算好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n舊年羅意庭一掂波噓到飛起，今季少左<br />\n講開永倫班臭雞，前年季後賽決賽，買飛咁啱買中永倫區，開波前義正派tee,咁我地梗係著啦，難得有氣氛嘛，點知打打下俾後面班女屌我地著黃衫做乜唔嗌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我直頭想叫佢要嗌留返係床嗌啦臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：永倫fans"},{"pid":"b91512b05c1aa1256cf172218d9354a9884b7430","tid":291073,"uid":111279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T18:43:23.000Z","msg":"ar Hong今日打成點?"},{"pid":"f5742ef501d1ca6d6aff5db3d6307dc67ecd73a2","tid":291073,"uid":56188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T01:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ar Hong今日打成點?</blockquote><br />\n無乜點出，兩球三分唔入"},{"pid":"b2b4db86febeabee90aa091fed39c964c24aec7d","tid":291073,"uid":28716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:17:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17206c9a5a47265c9f383a5dbc041a1b617366fd","tid":291073,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ar Hong今日打成點?</blockquote><br />\n無乜點出，兩球三分唔入</blockquote><br />\n傷左"},{"pid":"9942a76e74a3f82983e4dff65bd21e99b347d4ac","tid":291073,"uid":25771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:38:47.000Z","msg":"大家都上籃。。淨係吹一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a6c18b1da6e05796e5b0e0b3fc0b11996259f88","tid":291073,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:50:49.000Z","msg":"tyler字母哥上身"},{"pid":"f798597705b0724631250d9ec8fe8cd1581bae16","tid":291073,"uid":47007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"泰那今日搞咩,臨尾獨食mode竟然唔開<br />\n最好笑鬧隊友唔射外圍,跟住自己走去爆籃拎2分但仍然輸緊1分<br />\n同埋永倫打死果6,7條友,又唔係後生,應該俾南華騎死,東方如果操好D連總決賽都